{"tid":669494,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"韓女團開M字腿白褲走光 「駱駝蹄」清楚露出","createTime":"2018-05-18T13:22:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-19T04:16:57.000Z","uid":1221,"like":106,"dislike":76,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"a1de85887da4db8a816ca2e0687b23849f07d88d","tid":669494,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"南韓女子舞團Girl Crush日前上台飆舞時，表演過程被PO網瘋傳，然而意外引發討論的是，其中一名團員bomistry（보미）做出M字腿性感動作時，意外走光露出白色安全褲，進而導致私密部位型狀清楚外露，意外引發熱議。 <br />\n<br />\nGirl Crush於10日現身舞台演出，飆跳前「19禁成人女團」Stellar夯曲《Vibrato》，4團員各自穿上緊身激短裙，胸前挖空露出傲人事業線，裙子長度更是落在大腿根部附近，一個不注意，衣服就會隨著動作微微上拉，隨時陷入走光危機。 <br />\n<br />\n飆舞過程中，bomistry在進行M字腿、彎腰、躺地等性感動作時，惹火又養眼的畫面，讓粉絲鼻血直流，不過，她雖然頻頻調整裙子位置，不斷伸手往下拉，卻仍在跳舞過程中，露出裙子底下的白色安全褲，不少眼尖網友也發現，她下半身私密部位「駱駝趾」形狀，也因此清楚露出，意外掀起外界討論。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5afe18727d06cd2ed3ce9a06_201805180804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5afe18727d06cd2ed3ce9a06_201805180804.jpg&h=ea3f9add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RrgZ9ljauWI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRrgZ9ljauWI&d=V6JraWaE4za4%2B6keL3aCfMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ddd913c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RrgZ9ljauWI</a>"},{"pid":"987042810033447b6c93d2ca45f5d7bc05c6d1c9","tid":669494,"uid":51753,"like":153,"dislike":2,"score":151,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:28:07.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"327ccb758db8e36f2384360b71ddd39c0e670aa0","tid":669494,"uid":135767,"like":501,"dislike":5,"score":496,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f77c6847b8c57b3e81a3e8b03c3f5953ffee631e","tid":669494,"uid":29487,"like":216,"dislike":3,"score":213,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:30:20.