al/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80e0c95ba6e4db2e2da26d0afd8639cbbf93c178","tid":669494,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a1de85887da4db8a816ca2e0687b23849f07d88d","tid":669494,"uid":1221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T13:22:49.000Z","msg":"南韓女子舞團Girl Crush日前上台飆舞時，表演過程被PO網瘋傳，然而意外引發討論的是，其中一名團員bomistry（보미）做出M字腿性感動作時，意外走光露出白色安全褲，進而導致私密部位型狀清楚外露，意外引發熱議。 <br />\n<br />\nGirl Crush於10日現身舞台演出，飆跳前「19禁成人女團」Stellar夯曲《Vibrato》，4團員各自穿上緊身激短裙，胸前挖空露出傲人事業線，裙子長度更是落在大腿根部附近，一個不注意，衣服就會隨著動作微微上拉，隨時陷入走光危機。 <br />\n<br />\n飆舞過程中，bomistry在進行M字腿、彎腰、躺地等性感動作時，惹火又養眼的畫面，讓粉絲鼻血直流，不過，她雖然頻頻調整裙子位置，不斷伸手往下拉，卻仍在跳舞過程中，露出裙子底下的白色安全褲，不少眼尖網友也發現，她下半身私密部位「駱駝趾」形狀，也因此清楚露出，意外掀起外界討論。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imagelab.nownews.com/?w=1080&amp;q=85&amp;src=https://rssimg.nownews.com/images/5afe18727d06cd2ed3ce9a06_201805180804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimagelab.nownews.com%2F%3Fw%3D1080%26q%3D85%26src%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Frssimg.nownews.com%2Fimages%2F5afe18727d06cd2ed3ce9a06_201805180804.jpg&h=ea3f9add&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RrgZ9ljauWI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRrgZ9ljauWI&d=V6JraWaE4za4%2B6keL3aCfMn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=ddd913c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RrgZ9ljauWI</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T19:19:22.000Z","msg":"意外走光？"},{"pid":"d3b4b8ff4d4f5f6b67c7e56dfd244c86ebf87153","tid":669494,"uid":4156,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T20:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/19/042215_978dd230c852a8f372a437dd6552bf3e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F19%2F042215_978dd230c852a8f372a437dd6552bf3e.jpg&h=3348701